@URL_PREFIX = http://localhost:3001/api

### -------- GET /api/game/underground --------
### Test 1: return the underground map
GET {{URL_PREFIX}}/game/underground


### -------- GET /api/best-scores --------
### Test 1: ask for the first 10 best scores
GET {{URL_PREFIX}}/best-scores?begin=1&end=10

### Test 2: ask for the best scores
GET {{URL_PREFIX}}/best-scores?begin=1&end=1


### Test 3: wrong begin field
GET {{URL_PREFIX}}/best-scores?begin=-1&end=-1

### Test 4: wrong end field
GET {{URL_PREFIX}}/best-scores?begin=1&end=-1

### Test 5: missing parameters
GET {{URL_PREFIX}}/best-scores